  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业物联网的简单流程图，核心是两个组件：一个是现场的执行器控制器，另一个是边缘计算节点。我想用从左到右的布局。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，执行器控制器和边缘节点。这两个节点之间是什么关系？是数据流向，还是控制指令的传递？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是双向的数据交互关系，但图上我们先用一条无向的连接线表示它们之间的通信链路，不强调方向。节点命名就用IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController和IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画好了。左边是执行器控制器，右边是边缘节点，中间用一条线连接。你看看这个布局可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "log6",
        "log7"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说的不太准确。连接线应该是从执行器控制器指向边缘节点的，表示数据上报的方向。另外，节点标签显示的是完整名称，但内部标识用log6和log7这种简短形式对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "log6",
        "log7"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，您刚才说连接线要有方向，但之前又说用无向线表示通信链路。现在是要改成有向的箭头吗？还是保持无向但强调从左到右的流向？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "log6",
        "log7"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "抱歉我绕回来了，就保持无向的连接线吧，简单清晰。重点是表达这两个工业物联网组件的关联关系，方向不是关键。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "log6",
        "log7"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "确认最终版本：从左到右布局，左侧log6节点显示为IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController，右侧log7节点显示为IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode，两者用无向线连接。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "log6",
        "log7"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
